product_name: Guillow's Sky Streak Balsa Wood Power Plane - Package of 2
long_description: The Guillow's Sky Streak Balsa Wood Power Plane package of 2 brings back the nostalgia of timeless wooden toys. Planes feature rubber-band-powered wind-up props for high-flying fun. Balsa-wood planes come with easy assembly instructions.
